                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            {% comment %} Step 2 - Summary {% endcomment %}
            <div id="vpc-step-2" class="vpc-step-2">
              <h2 class="vpc-step-2__heading">Samenvatting</h2>
              
              <div class="vpc-step-2__section">
                <div class="vpc-step-2__section-header">
                  <h3 class="vpc-step-2__section-heading">Basisprijs</h3>
                  <span class="vpc-step-2__section-price" id="vpc-summary-base-price">€49.950</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="vpc-step-2__section">
                <div class="vpc-step-2__section-header">
                  <h3 class="vpc-step-2__section-heading">Woonserre configuratie</h3>
                </div>
                <table class="vpc-table" id="vpc-summary-table">
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <th class="vpc-table__heading">Afmetingen</th>
                      <td class="vpc-table__value" id="summary-dimensions">200 x 450 cm (9 m²)</td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>

              <div class="vpc-step-2__form">
                <div class="vpc-step-2__form-group">
                  <h4>Heeft u een achterom?</h4>
                  <p class="vpc-step-2__form-description">Als u geen achterom heeft, moeten we een extra kraan inhuren om de heimachine en graafmachine op zijn plek te krijgen</p>
                  <div class="vpc-step-2__radio-options">
                    <input type="radio" id="achterom-ja" name="achterom" value="Wel een achterom" checked>
                    <label class="radio-label" for="achterom-ja">
                      <span class="radio-label__text">Wel een achterom</span>
                      <span class="radio-label__price"></span>
                    </label>
                    <input type="radio" id="achterom-nee" name="achterom" value="Geen achterom" data-price="2250">
                    <label class="radio-label" for="achterom-nee">
                      <span class="radio-label__text">Geen achterom</span>
                      <span class="radio-label__price">+€2.250</span>
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="vpc-step-2__form-group">
                  <h4>Achtergevel doorbreken?</h4>
                  <div class="vpc-step-2__radio-options">
                    <input type="radio" id="doorbraak-nee" name="doorbraak" value="Geen doorbraak" checked>
                    <label class="radio-label" for="doorbraak-nee">
                      <span class="radio-label__text">Geen doorbraak</span>
                      <span class="radio-label__price"></span>
                    </label>
                    <input type="radio" id="doorbraak-ja" name="doorbraak" value="Wel een doorbraak" data-price="3500">
                    <label class="radio-label" for="doorbraak-ja">
                      <span class="radio-label__text">Wel een doorbraak</span>
                      <span class="radio-label__price">+€3.500</span>
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="vpc-step-2__form-group">
                  <h4>Wat is uw postcode?</h4>
                  <p class="vpc-step-2__form-description">Kilometervergoeding transport</p>
                  <input type="text" id="postcode-input" name="postcode" placeholder="1234AB" required>
                  <div class="zipcode-calculator">
                    <div class="zipcode-calculator__row">
                      <span class="zipcode-calculator__label">Afstand:</span>
                      <span class="zipcode-calculator__value" id="zipcode-distance">-- km</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="zipcode-calculator__row">
                      <span class="zipcode-calculator__label">Transportkosten:</span>
                      <span class="zipcode-calculator__value" id="zipcode-cost">€0</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <p class="zipcode-error" id="zipcode-error"></p>
                </div>
              </div>

              {% comment %} Step 2 Navigation {% endcomment %}
              <div class="vpc-step-navigation">
                <button type="button" class="c-button c-button--box c-button--outline vpc-prev-step" onclick="VPCWoonserreConfigurator.goToStep(1)">
                  Vorige stap
                </button>
                <button type="button" class="c-button c-button--box c-button--box-colorone vpc-next-step" onclick="VPCWoonserreConfigurator.goToStep(3)">
                  Volgende stap
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>

            {% comment %} Step 3 - Quote Request Form {% endcomment %}
            <div id="vpc-step-3" class="vpc-step-3">
              <h2>Offerte aanvragen</h2>
              <p>Volledige ontwerp per mail ontvangen? Laat hieronder je gegevens achter. Zijn er na ontvangst bepaalde wensen niet opgenomen? Laat het ons weten, dan plannen we een bezichtiging in.</p>
              
              <ul class="list--checkmarks">
                <li class="list__item">Ontvang je 3D-ontwerp per mail</li>
                <li class="list__item">Zie alle opties op een rijtje</li>
                <li class="list__item">Pas op locatie je wensen aan</li>
              </ul>

              <form id="rqa_form" action="/contact#contact_form" method="post" accept-charset="UTF-8">
                <input type="hidden" name="form_type" value="contact">
                <input type="hidden" name="utf8" value="✓">
                <input type="hidden" name="contact[product_type]" value="Woonserre">
                <input type="hidden" name="contact[configuration]" id="rqa_configuration" value="">
                <input type="hidden" name="contact[total_price]" id="rqa_total_price" value="">

                <div class="form-group">
                  <input type="text" id="rqa_name" name="contact[name]" placeholder="Naam *" required>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <input type="text" id="rqa_address" name="contact[address]" placeholder="Straat + Huisnummer *" required>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <input type="text" id="rqa_city" name="contact[city]" placeholder="Woonplaats *" required>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <input type="text" id="rqa_phone" name="contact[phone]" placeholder="Telefoon *" required>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <input type="email" id="rqa_email" name="contact[email]" placeholder="Email *" required>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <textarea id="rqa_message" name="contact[body]" rows="4" placeholder="Vragen en/of opmerkingen"></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="vpc-showroom-section">
                  <h4>Interesse in showroom afspraak?</h4>
                  <p>Wil je onze woonserre opties in het echt zien? Kom dan langs bij ons op locatie in omgeving Amsterdam. Je ziet de verschillende mogelijkheden en kunt direct al je vragen stellen.</p>
                  <div class="vpc-showroom-group">
                    <label class="vpc-showroom-checkbox">
                      <input type="checkbox" name="contact[showroom]" value="Ja, ik wil graag een showroom afspraak maken">
                      <span>Ja, ik wil graag een showroom afspraak maken</span>
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <p class="disclaimer-link">
                  Door verder te gaan gaat u akkoord met ons <a href="{{ section.settings.privacy_page | default: '/pages/privacybeleid' }}" target="_blank">privacy beleid</a>
                </p>
              </form>

              {% comment %} Step 3 Navigation {% endcomment %}
              <div class="vpc-step-navigation">
                <button type="button" class="c-button c-button--box c-button--outline vpc-prev-step" onclick="VPCWoonserreConfigurator.goToStep(2)">
                  Vorige stap
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>

            {% comment %} Sidebar Floating Price Banner (for step 2/3) {% endcomment %}
            <div id="vpc-sidebar-price-container" class="vpc-sidebar-price-container">
              <div class="vpc-price-center">
                <span class="vpc-price-label">Totaal woonserre (incl. btw)</span>
                <span class="vpc-sidebar-price vpc-price-value">€49.950</span>
              </div>
              <div class="vpc-price-link">
                <span class="vpc-value-text">Waardevermeerdering weten?</span>
                <button type="button" class="vpc-value-check-btn" onclick="VPCWoonserreConfigurator.openValuePopup()">Check</button>
              </div>
              <div class="vpc-price-buttons">
                <button type="button" class="vpc-prev-step-btn vpc-sidebar-prev-btn" onclick="VPCWoonserreConfigurator.goToPreviousStep()">
                  Terug
                </button>
                <button type="button" class="c-button c-button--box c-button--box-colorone vpc-next-step-btn vpc-sidebar-next-btn" onclick="VPCWoonserreConfigurator.goToNextStep()">
                  Volgende stap
                </button>
                <button type="submit" form="rqa_form" class="c-button c-button--box c-button--box-colorone vpc-next-step-btn vpc-sidebar-submit-btn" style="display: none;">
                  Offerte aanvragen
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        {% comment %} Preview Container {% endcomment %}
        <div id="vpc-preview-wrap" class="vpc-preview-wrap">
          <div id="vpc-preview-container" class="vpc-preview-container">
            <div class="s-configurator-container__preview-images">
              
              {% comment %} Exterior Preview Images {% endcomment %}
              <div class="s-configurator-container__exterior-images">
                {% comment %} Base exterior image {% endcomment %}
                <div class="c-image c-image--base exterior-element" style="z-index: 0">
                  {% if section.settings.base_exterior_image %}
                    <img src="{{ section.settings.base_exterior_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}" 
                         alt="Woonserre buitenaanzicht" 
                         loading="lazy">
                  {% else %}
                    <img src="https://deprefabriek.nl/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/PDF-glass-extension-001-1800x1350.png" 
                         alt="Woonserre buitenaanzicht" 
                         loading="lazy">
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
                {% comment %} Dynamic option images will be added here via JavaScript {% endcomment %}
              </div>

              {% comment %} Interior Preview Images {% endcomment %}
              <div class="s-configurator-container__interior-images" style="display: none;">
                {% comment %} Base interior image {% endcomment %}
                <div class="c-image c-image--base interior-element" style="z-index: 0">
                  {% if section.settings.base_interior_image %}
                    <img src="{{ section.settings.base_interior_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}" 
                         alt="Woonserre binnenaanzicht" 
                         loading="lazy">
                  {% else %}
                    <img src="https://deprefabriek.nl/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/PDF-glass-extension-interior-001-1800x1350.png" 
                         alt="Woonserre binnenaanzicht" 
                         loading="lazy">
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
                {% comment %} Dynamic option images will be added/updated here via JavaScript {% endcomment %}
              </div>

            </div>
            
            {% comment %} Help Button - Outside floating banner {% endcomment %}
            <div class="vpc-price-help">
              <button type="button" class="vpc-help-button">
                <span class="vpc-help-icon">?</span>
                <span class="vpc-help-text">Hulp bij de configurator?</span>
              </button>
            </div>
            
            {% comment %} Floating Price Banner {% endcomment %}
            <div id="vpc-price-container" class="vpc-price-container">
              <div class="vpc-price-center">
                <span class="vpc-price-label">Totaal woonserre (incl. btw)</span>
                <span id="vpc-price" class="vpc-price-value">€49.950</span>
              </div>
              <div class="vpc-price-link">
                <span class="vpc-value-text">Waardevermeerdering weten?</span>
                <button type="button" class="vpc-value-check-btn" onclick="VPCWoonserreConfigurator.openValuePopup()">Check</button>
              </div>
              <div class="vpc-price-buttons">
                <button type="button" class="vpc-prev-step-btn" onclick="VPCWoonserreConfigurator.goToPreviousStep()" style="display: none;">
                  Terug
                </button>
                <button type="button" class="c-button c-button--box c-button--box-colorone vpc-next-step-btn" onclick="VPCWoonserreConfigurator.goToNextStep()">
                  Volgende stap
                </button>
              </div>
              <input type="hidden" id="vpc-total-price-result" value="€49.950" name="Total price" required>
            </div>
            
            {% comment %} View Switcher - Exterior/Interior {% endcomment %}
            <div class="vpc-preview__switcher">
              <button type="button" class="vpc-preview__switcher-btn vpc-preview__switcher-btn--exterior active" data-view="exterior" onclick="VPCWoonserreConfigurator.switchView('exterior')">
                Buitenzijde
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="vpc-preview__switcher-btn vpc-preview__switcher-btn--interior" data-view="interior" onclick="VPCWoonserreConfigurator.switchView('interior')">
                Binnenzijde
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

